description: I was so excited to revisit one of Ricky's classics. Sometimes I feel less is more, and in this case, removing music, adding never before seen footage and letting Ricky's breathing be the soundtrack, I think I made this one a lot more exciting to watch than the original release. In my opinion it's a brand new scene and a must see for all of Ricky's fans!
title: Ricky's Big Muscle - Director's Cut
